snippet.title: Ace Combat 7: Skies Unknown - PS4/XB1/PC - Golden Joystick Awards Trailer
snippet.description:
The skies of Strangereal are about to become the stage of the fiercest dogfights. Are you prepared to do what it takes to win the war? Watch this intense new trailer revealed at the Golden Joystick Awards!
ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN takes off on January 18, 2019 on PS4 and XB1 and on February 1, 2019 on PC. 
Pre-order: https://fcld.ly/ac7preorder
